The term '''lolicon''' (short for [[lolita|lolita complex]]) is slang for the feminine [[CP]] [[hentai]] genre. The male equivalent is known as [[shotacon]], but you already know that, you [[sick fuck]]. For those that like 'em really young, please also give [[Toddlercon]] a gander. It may be soul-crushingly horrible, but [[no|at least it's better]] than [[guro]].

How anyone can get off to [[Loli-chan|little girls]] that look like little boys; [[it is a mystery|no one knows]]. What we do know is, there's enough lolicon on our beloved [[Internet]] to fill a goddamn supercomputer. [[John Solomon|Masturbating to lolicon is bad, and you should feel bad]] for it. Slang amongst fans (also termed lolicons, the subject matter itself is simply '''loli''') include acronyms like [[DFC]] for '''delicious flat chest''', a predilection for [[pantsu]], and a predominance of fandom for anime & video games starring various immortal inhuman girl characters such as [[alien]]s, [[angel]]s [[Dan Brown|&]] [[demon]]s, [[elf|elves]], [[god]]esses, [[robot]]s, [[transformers]] or [[vampire]]s as it provides the "she's [[At least 100 years|an adult]], don't judge her by her looks" escape clause.

